00:34:00.855 --> 00:34:03.554
and I opened my eyes, and I was completely alone in the car,

656
00:34:03.554 --> 00:34:06.017
and I pulled the steering wheel back,

657
00:34:06.017 --> 00:34:09.153
and I just barely, barely got back from the edge

658
00:34:09.153 --> 00:34:11.415
of the embankment there.

