662
00:34:20.715 --> 00:34:23.338
very fast about two inches in front of my face.

663
00:34:23.338 --> 00:34:24.811
<v ->We were building this new antenna,</v>

664
00:34:24.811 --> 00:34:28.416
and we needed a place to put a guywire

