00:34:48.180 --> 00:34:50.889
and all kinds of tests on me and they just shook their

674
00:34:50.889 --> 00:34:52.735
head and you know, they keep saying,

675
00:34:52.735 --> 00:34:54.377
"How many volts was that?"

