751
00:38:16.459 --> 00:38:17.972
so that they did not function.

752
00:38:17.972 --> 00:38:19.710
They just hung limply.

753
00:38:20.810 --> 00:38:22.555
They gave me a prognosis, ultimately,

754
00:38:22.555 --> 00:38:24.742
that said that I would not recover,

755
00:38:24.742 --> 00:38:27.504
and that the speech that I was able to generate,

756
00:38:27.504 --> 00:38:30.384
I was generating with some fatty tissues

757
00:38:30.384 --> 00:38:31.406
that were called false chords

758
00:38:31.406 --> 00:38:32.462
that are in your throat, but they're not

759
00:38:32.462 --> 00:38:35.587
designed to sustain speech, and they told me that

760
00:38:35.587 --> 00:38:39.242
ultimately, I would wear away the false chords surfaces

761
00:38:39.242 --> 00:38:41.086
to the point that they could no longer get together

762
00:38:41.086 --> 00:38:42.900
and I would be totally mute.

763
00:38:42.900 --> 00:38:46.452
They predicted that should all occur by late '94

764
00:38:46.452 --> 00:38:49.972
or early '95, I should be totally mute.

765
00:38:49.972 --> 00:38:51.316
That was their word.

766
00:38:51.316 --> 00:38:53.492
All of that is observable on video tape.

767
00:38:53.492 --> 00:38:57.150
The doctors ran like timelapse photography.

768
00:38:57.150 --> 00:38:59.016
Every time I would go see them, they would

769
00:38:59.016 --> 00:39:01.352
put the scope down my throat and record all of that.

770
00:39:01.352 --> 00:39:05.946
So you could watch scar tissue actually form in my throat.

771
00:39:05.946 --> 00:39:08.709
My wife became the breadwinner of our family

772
00:39:08.709 --> 00:39:10.885
because we had to resign the pastorate where we were.

773
00:39:10.885 --> 00:39:12.303
I could no longer preach.

774
00:39:12.303 --> 00:39:13.263
I couldn't sustain that.

775
00:39:13.263 --> 00:39:15.951
I couldn't go to a sales job because I couldn't make

776
00:39:15.951 --> 00:39:17.370
whole calls because I sounded like an obscene

777
00:39:17.370 --> 00:39:20.687
phone caller, and the people would hang up on me.

778
00:39:21.997 --> 00:39:23.897
You know, you laugh about that now and it's amusing,

779
00:39:23.897 --> 00:39:27.214
but at the time, it's extremely frustrating.

780
00:39:28.624 --> 00:39:30.588
Emotionally, I was destroyed.

781
00:39:30.588 --> 00:39:32.710
Career-wise, I was set aside.

782
00:39:32.710 --> 00:39:35.099
In many of the things that I thought

783
00:39:35.099 --> 00:39:37.894
were important in my life, I found myself at loose ends,

784
00:39:37.894 --> 00:39:41.553
and like other people, I asked God, "Why, why?"

785
00:39:43.363 --> 00:39:46.267
<v ->He was not expecting for God to heal him</v>

786
00:39:46.267 --> 00:39:48.528
at any given moment, and one day,

787
00:39:48.528 --> 00:39:50.085
he was teaching a Sunday school class,

788
00:39:50.085 --> 00:39:52.347
filling in for someone using a special microphone

789
00:39:52.347 --> 00:39:54.981
so that his listeners could catch his words.

790
00:39:54.981 --> 00:39:56.325
And he's rasping into the microphone,

791
00:39:56.325 --> 00:40:00.937
and as he's teaching about God out of Psalm 103

792
00:40:00.937 --> 00:40:03.738
how God forgives our sins and heals our diseases

793
00:40:03.738 --> 00:40:07.610
and redeems our life from the pit, something broke.

794
00:40:07.610 --> 00:40:10.447
In a church of 24,000 members,

795
00:40:10.447 --> 00:40:14.126
that's the only class that taped Sunday school lessons.

796
00:40:14.126 --> 00:40:16.046
So it was caught on tape.

797
00:40:16.046 --> 00:40:19.267
On the other hand, to say that since we don't have

798
00:40:19.267 --> 00:40:21.582
anything after the Book of Acts that miracles

799
00:40:21.582 --> 00:40:26.126
in the Book of Acts never happen again is equally as wrong.

800
00:40:26.126 --> 00:40:29.454
Because you have put God in a box both ways.

801
00:40:29.454 --> 00:40:31.032
He doesn't want to be in the box.

802
00:40:31.032 --> 00:40:33.863
So to Psalm, he says, I'm excited.

803
00:40:33.863 --> 00:40:35.623
Bless the Lord, Oh my soul.

804
00:40:35.623 --> 00:40:40.623
One of his best is he heals all of my diseases.

805
00:40:40.856 --> 00:40:42.658
And then in verse four he says,

806
00:40:42.658 --> 00:40:47.266
and he redeems my life from the pit.

807
00:40:47.266 --> 00:40:50.806
And I like that verse just a whole lot.

808
00:40:50.806 --> 00:40:54.604
I have had and you have had in times

809
00:40:54.604 --> 00:40:57.783
past pit experiences.

810
00:41:01.233 --> 00:41:06.233
We've both had, we've all had times when

811
00:41:06.891 --> 00:41:11.891
our life seemed to be in a pit, in a grave,

812
00:41:12.032 --> 00:41:17.032
and we he didn't have an answer for ... (deeply inhales)

813
00:41:21.131 --> 00:41:25.457
the pit we find ourselves in, (deeply inhales)

814
00:41:26.880 --> 00:41:30.026
And I don't understand this right now.

815
00:41:30.026 --> 00:41:33.951
(crowd laughs and applauds)

816
00:41:35.101 --> 00:41:40.101
I'm a bit overwhelmed at the moment.

817
00:41:41.958 --> 00:41:46.158
(hoarse breathing)

818
00:41:47.369 --> 00:41:51.326
I'm not quite sure what to say or do.

819
00:41:52.146 --> 00:41:55.655
(crowd cries and cheers in background)

820
00:41:56.165 --> 00:42:00.311
(deeply inhales)

821
00:42:05.331 --> 00:42:10.331
I'm (chuckles) sounds funny to say,

822
00:42:11.090 --> 00:42:13.352
a loss for words.

823
00:42:13.352 --> 00:42:16.759
(crowd laughs and cheers)

824
00:42:21.532 --> 00:42:23.517
And I have to tell you, I still am at a loss for words.

825
00:42:24.658 --> 00:42:26.033
<v ->The people in that Sunday school class</v>

826
00:42:26.033 --> 00:42:29.745
began to weep and clap and some were silent.

827
00:42:29.745 --> 00:42:31.526
Some were laughing.

828
00:42:31.526 --> 00:42:34.268
There was just an explosion of joy.

829
00:42:34.268 --> 00:42:35.953
<v ->That moment was wonderful,</v>

830
00:42:35.953 --> 00:42:38.513
and I thank God for what occurred,

831
00:42:38.513 --> 00:42:41.041
but the miracle doesn't end there.

832
00:42:41.041 --> 00:42:42.576
You see, I've been back to the doctor's,

833
00:42:42.576 --> 00:42:44.688
and when I went back and they showed me the last piece

834
00:42:44.688 --> 00:42:46.683
of videotape that they shot of my throat,

835
00:42:46.683 --> 00:42:49.147
it shows that the scar tissue that had formed

836
00:42:49.147 --> 00:42:52.293
there is gone, and it's as slick smooth in the bottom

837
00:42:52.293 --> 00:42:55.290
of my throat as the day it all began.

838
00:42:55.290 --> 00:42:57.829
Scar tissue doesn't disappear.

839
00:42:57.829 --> 00:42:59.791
So even if you could coincidentally explain

840
00:42:59.791 --> 00:43:03.471
how I'm able to speak, what happened to the scar tissue?

841
00:43:03.471 --> 00:43:05.384
That's the miracle.

842
00:43:10.078 --> 00:43:12.473
<v Voiceover>These stories have provoked questions</v>

843
00:43:12.473 --> 00:43:15.033
in the minds of those who have experienced them.

844
00:43:15.033 --> 00:43:17.124
Were these miracles?

845
00:43:17.124 --> 00:43:20.099
And if so, what do they say about life

846
00:43:20.099 --> 00:43:23.011
and the existence of a creator?

847
00:43:23.011 --> 00:43:26.275
These questions stare back at them, across the canyon

848
00:43:26.275 --> 00:43:30.029
which divides faith from rational explanation,

849
00:43:30.029 --> 00:43:34.268
and they have been left trying to find a bridge.

850
00:43:36.109 --> 00:43:39.298
<v ->I do know that our life moves in the direction</v>

851
00:43:39.298 --> 00:43:42.498
of our most dominant thoughts.

852
00:43:42.498 --> 00:43:44.119
I think miracles.

853
00:43:44.119 --> 00:43:46.924
I think and believe for answers,

854
00:43:46.924 --> 00:43:49.207
and there have been times in my own life

855
00:43:49.207 --> 00:43:54.207
when I've been basically bankrupt and know which way to go,

856
00:43:54.241 --> 00:43:58.422
and miracles happen, just right out of the blue,

857
00:43:58.422 --> 00:44:00.726
and so I get excited about that because

858
00:44:00.726 --> 00:44:02.891
I know that God cares for us.

859
00:44:02.891 --> 00:44:07.606
<v ->Love is where God is, and if God is right here,</v>

860
00:44:07.606 --> 00:44:09.942
then love should be right here too.

861
00:44:09.942 --> 00:44:12.149
And it's all connected in a way.

862
00:44:12.149 --> 00:44:14.555
I think he shows us that as he

863
00:44:14.555 --> 00:44:16.979
performs these marvelous miracles,

864
00:44:16.979 --> 00:44:19.454
these little signs and wonders for us.

865
00:44:19.454 --> 00:44:22.792
The whole point of it is, I'm here and I love you.

866
00:44:22.792 --> 00:44:24.094
<v ->Faith, hope, and love.</v>

867
00:44:24.094 --> 00:44:26.515
Wonderful chemistry.

868
00:44:26.515 --> 00:44:28.392
Hope is an attitude, you see?

869
00:44:28.392 --> 00:44:29.800
Fear is an attitude.

870
00:44:29.800 --> 00:44:33.367
So the people who have no hope,

871
00:44:33.367 --> 00:44:36.744
lots of fear, no faith, and no love.

872
00:44:36.744 --> 00:44:39.421
What are they foreseeing?

873
00:44:39.421 --> 00:44:41.437
They live out what they foresee,

874
00:44:41.437 --> 00:44:43.175
which is death and suffering.

875
00:44:43.175 --> 00:44:45.116
And that's why there are physicians

876
00:44:45.116 --> 00:44:47.815
who can enhance death, you see,

877
00:44:47.815 --> 00:44:49.905
if every time you come to an office,

878
00:44:49.905 --> 00:44:51.857
your hope is taken away,

879
00:44:51.857 --> 00:44:54.044
love is poo-pooed, and there's nothing

880
00:44:54.044 --> 00:44:56.241
to have faith in except the doctor.

881
00:44:56.241 --> 00:44:58.022
You're going to die right on schedule,

882
00:44:58.022 --> 00:44:59.686
and the doctor says, "See, I told you.

883
00:44:59.686 --> 00:45:01.467
"What are you talking about, miracles?"

884
00:45:01.467 --> 00:45:02.939
Then you walk into another office,

885
00:45:02.939 --> 00:45:05.168
and the doctor says, "I love you.

886
00:45:05.168 --> 00:45:06.587
"What would you like to do?

887
00:45:06.587 --> 00:45:09.232
"Let me tell you what other people have done

888
00:45:09.232 --> 00:45:11.547
"who have exceeded our expectations."

889
00:45:11.547 --> 00:45:15.909
<v ->I think the more love you can put out,</v>

890
00:45:15.909 --> 00:45:17.712
the more love you're going to receive.

891
00:45:17.712 --> 00:45:20.911
This goes back to the idea of the response of universe.

892
00:45:20.911 --> 00:45:24.687
Certainly, if you put out love into the universe

893
00:45:24.687 --> 00:45:27.386
and if you can put out unconditional love,

894
00:45:27.386 --> 00:45:30.127
you're going to receive unconditional love.

895
00:45:30.127 --> 00:45:34.969
<v ->I feel sometimes that all that is between</v>

896
00:45:34.969 --> 00:45:39.969
our wishes and God to accomplish what he wants for us,

897
00:45:40.366 --> 00:45:43.513
what he has planned for us is our prayer.

898
00:45:43.513 --> 00:45:47.011
That's all that is missing and he wants us to pray.

899
00:45:47.011 --> 00:45:49.400
<v ->It's a free thing that God gives us.</v>

900
00:45:49.400 --> 00:45:52.515
Free blessings everyday, free miracles.

901
00:45:52.515 --> 00:45:55.437
You don't have to earn this.

902
00:45:55.437 --> 00:45:59.959
There's nothing you can do to earn his love.

903
00:45:59.959 --> 00:46:02.125
<v ->We know that he loves us,</v>

904
00:46:02.125 --> 00:46:04.129
and that he does want the very best for us.

905
00:46:04.129 --> 00:46:07.863
<v ->The public way in which this occurred in my life</v>

906
00:46:07.863 --> 00:46:12.002
was for the purpose of saying to all those around me

907
00:46:12.002 --> 00:46:14.284
I care about you as much as I care about Duane.

908
00:46:14.284 --> 00:46:15.884
I'm just as concerned about your prayers.

909
00:46:15.884 --> 00:46:17.100
They mean something.

910
00:46:17.100 --> 00:46:19.009
So I tell folks today when you pray for somebody,

911
00:46:19.009 --> 00:46:20.300
don't stop praying because you don't know

912
00:46:20.300 --> 00:46:25.185
when that moment might be that the change will occur.

913
00:46:25.185 --> 00:46:26.625
Don't give up.

914
00:46:26.625 --> 00:46:27.499
Dont' quit.

915
00:46:27.499 --> 00:46:28.858
It's not over.

916
00:46:30.720 --> 00:46:35.720
(uplifting flute music)